<ab facs="#facs_126_r1l17">vvie Jr 
<add><ab facs="#facs_126_r1l16"><expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan> </ab></add> v̈llein Ruſʒwurm cʒu küllwingen <expan>ſeine<ex>m</ex></expan> <expan>Armman<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_126_r1l18">den Er mit tür vnd tor beſlieſʒ iij kẅ vnd Ochſen . 
<del rend="strikethrough">Als Jr </del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_126_r1l19">genomen habt . <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> daʒ Jr dem <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan> <expan>B<ex>urgers</ex></expan> <expan>Armman<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
